      "date": "2015-09-10 18:19:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nIs the ext4 deadlock bug also present in upstream ext4 or is the locking specific to osd-ldiskfs?  If present upstream please also send the patch to linux-ext4 mailing list.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "d26477c2a0b637a17795b0e0462dd55467b182b5",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 443,
        "name": "Andrew Perepechko",
        "email": "andrew.perepechko@hpe.com",
        "username": "panda"
      },
      "date": "2015-09-10 18:59:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis deadlock was discussed on the kernel list, e.g.\nhttp://lists.openwall.net/linux-ext4/2012/11/09/4\nIt was fixed by commit b3aff3e3f61d13586fd46d1ee6f7353ab3050b6d\n(ext4: reimplement fiemap using extent status tree) which first appeared in vanilla kernel v 3.8 (based on git describe --contains).",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
